metadata.name: INSURGENT 🔰 Street stickers. #4809
metadata.description:
I'm an urban artist exploring the world of NFTs, and I'm excited to showcase my latest collection of generative art trained by my hand-drawn mecha urban stickers. If you enjoy, please consider supporting my experimental digital journey .

 [Starting on NFT World, please Follow me 🔰 ](https://twitter.com/nftinsurgent)

It would be great if you wanted to print any of them as a sticker,  just an idea ...
